data.description: Immaculate condition is what you will find in this beautiful "Cal Desert Modern" style home. Updated kitchen with granite counters. Vaulted ceilings with beams. Wood floors, brick fireplace and fresh paint inside and out!! Roomy floor plan. Enjoy the summer nights under the covered patio admiring all the landscape! Underground sprinklers. There is a 10X12 garden shed, plus an added bonus with an insulated "Man Cave" off the back of the carport. Call today to View!!
